18
00:01:01,795 --> 00:01:04,059
**<i>In perfect moments</i> **
<i>[Continues, Indistinct]</i>

19
00:01:04,130 --> 00:01:06,826
<i>[Man Narrating]</i>
<i>Among other things, many other things...</i>

20
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:10,233
<i>my old professor loved to eat.</i>

21
00:01:10,303 --> 00:01:13,272
There he is!
What do you say?

22
00:01:13,339 --> 00:01:15,273
**<i>Sleep, baby, sleep</i> **

23
